  "summary": {
    "as": "Passed House amended", 
    "date": "1982-05-10", 
    "text": "(Measure passed House, amended) Piracy and Counterfeiting Amendments Act of 1982 - Increases the criminal penalties for the transportation, sale, or receipt of phonograph records bearing forged or counterfeit labels. Increases criminal penalties for the willful infringement of a copyright for commercial advantage or private financial gain involving a specified number of phonorecords, motion pictures or audiovisual works, or sound recordings."
  }, 
